headline: Is It Time To Reassess United Parcel Service (UPS) After Recent Share Price Rebound?
summary: If you are looking at United Parcel Service and wondering whether the current share price reflects its true worth, this article will walk through what the numbers are really saying about value. The stock recently closed at US$115.96, with returns of 9.2% over the last 30 days, 14.8% year to date, 4.1% over 1 year, and longer term returns of a 26.9% decline over 3 years and a 12.6% decline over 5 years that many investors may want to put in context.
